#: ../../language/error_codes/E4198.md:1
msgid "E4198"
msgstr "E4198"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4198.md:3
msgid "Compiler diagnostic name: `struct_constr_not_implemented`."
msgstr "编译器诊断名称：`struct_constr_not_implemented`。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4198.md:5
msgid ""
"When a `struct` declares a constructor signature, that constructor must "
"be implemented as the corresponding `Type::new` method. The declaration "
"only gives the constructor signature; it does not create the "
"implementation body."
msgstr ""
"当 `struct` 声明构造器签名时，必须将该构造器实现为对应的 `Type::new` 方法。"
"声明只给出构造器签名，并不会创建实现体。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4198.md:9
msgid "Erroneous example"
msgstr "错误示例"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4198.md:11
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"priv struct Point {\n"
"  x : Int\n"
"\n"
"  fn new(Int) -> Point\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4198.md:15
msgid "Suggestion"
msgstr "建议"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4198.md:17
msgid "Define the matching `Type::new` method."
msgstr "定义匹配的 `Type::new` 方法。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4198.md:19
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"priv struct Point {\n"
"  x : Int\n"
"\n"
"  fn new(Int) -> Point\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"fn Point::new(x : Int) -> Point {\n"
"  { x, }\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"test {\n"
"  let point = Point(4)\n"
"  inspect(point.x, content=\"4\")\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

